Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:16.360
There are three primary colors.

00:00:16.360 --> 00:00:19.240
They are red and yellow and blue!

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:25.620
When any two colors are mixed together,
they make a brand new color for you!

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:29.070
There are three secondary colors.

00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:31.710
Yellow and blue together make green!

00:00:32.080 --> 00:00:33.580
Red and yellow make orange!

00:00:33.580 --> 00:00:35.600
Red and blue make purple!

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:38.760
Colors that you all have seen!

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:40.300
(We all have seen.)

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:43.180
Colors make everything beautiful.

00:00:43.180 --> 00:00:46.560
Colors bring joy to our eyes.

00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:49.420
The colors of flowers,
of leaves in the fall,

00:00:49.480 --> 00:00:56.480
a sunset, a rainbow,
and beautiful blue skies!

00:00:56.480 --> 00:00:58.820
Then there's black, brown, gray, and white.

00:00:58.830 --> 00:01:02.590
Colors that you see every day.

00:01:02.590 --> 00:01:03.470
Dirt is brown.

00:01:03.470 --> 00:01:04.310
Snow is white.

00:01:04.310 --> 00:01:05.950
The night sky is black.

00:01:05.950 --> 00:01:08.970
Rain clouds and dolphins, they are gray!

00:01:08.970 --> 00:01:12.190
When you look all around you see colors!

00:01:12.190 --> 00:01:15.450
No matter where you go, there they are.

00:01:15.450 --> 00:01:18.320
It's so much fun to learn about colors.

00:01:18.440 --> 00:01:21.880
They're all around us, near and far!

